@startuml t_sequence_06_autonumber_dividers_box_ref
title Sequence Diagram — Autonumber, Dividers, Delays, Spacers, Box, Ref, Newpage

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' BOX declarations wrap participants visually
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

box "Frontend" #EEF2FF
    participant "Browser" as BR
    participant "Web App" as WA
end box

box "Backend Services" #E8F5E9
    participant "API GW"  as GW
    participant "Auth"    as AU
    participant "Orders"  as OR
end box

box "Data Layer" #FFF8E1
    participant "Primary DB" as PDB
    participant "Cache"      as CA
end box

participant "External\nPayment API" as PAY

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 1. AUTONUMBER — basic form
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== autonumber (plain) ==

autonumber

BR -> WA : loadPage()
WA -> GW : GET /api/orders
GW -> AU : validateSession()
AU --> GW : valid
GW -> OR : fetchOrders()
OR -> PDB : SELECT * FROM orders
PDB --> OR : rows
OR --> GW : order list
GW --> WA : JSON response
WA --> BR : render page

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 2. AUTONUMBER START VALUE
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== autonumber with start value ==

autonumber 100

BR -> GW : request 100
GW --> BR : response 101

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 3. AUTONUMBER START + INCREMENT
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== autonumber start + increment ==

autonumber 10 10

BR -> GW : request (10)
GW -> AU : check (20)
AU --> GW : ok (30)
GW --> BR : done (40)

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 4. AUTONUMBER WITH FORMAT STRING
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== autonumber format string ==

autonumber "<b>[000]</b>"

BR -> GW : formatted [001]
GW -> AU : formatted [002]
AU --> GW : formatted [003]
GW --> BR : formatted [004]

== autonumber with custom format ==

autonumber 1 1 "<font color=blue><b>Message ##</b></font>"

BR -> WA : msg 1
WA -> GW : msg 2
GW --> WA : msg 3
WA --> BR : msg 4

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 5. AUTONUMBER STOP / RESUME
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== autonumber stop ==

autonumber 1

BR -> GW : numbered 1
GW --> BR : numbered 2

autonumber stop

BR -> WA : unnumbered
WA --> BR : unnumbered

autonumber resume

BR -> GW : resumed (3)
GW --> BR : resumed (4)

== autonumber resume with new increment ==

autonumber stop
BR -> AU : stop gap
AU --> BR : not numbered

autonumber resume 5

BR -> GW : resumed with inc=5 (9)
GW --> BR : continued (14)

== autonumber resume with format ==

autonumber stop

autonumber resume 2 "<i>(%d)</i>"

BR -> GW : italic format
GW --> BR : italic format

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 6. DIVIDERS  == text ==
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

autonumber stop

== Simple divider ==

BR -> GW : step A
GW --> BR : result A

== Divider with longer text label here ==

BR -> GW : step B
GW --> BR : result B

== 特殊文字 Divider with Unicode ==

BR -> GW : unicode step
GW --> BR : unicode result

== ==

' Empty divider (just == ==) — edge case
BR -> GW : after empty divider
GW --> BR : ok

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 7. DELAYS  ...  and  ... text ...
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== Delays ==

BR -> PAY : initiatePayment()
activate PAY

...

PAY --> BR : paymentPending

... 5 minutes later ...

PAY -> PDB : commitTransaction()
activate PDB
PDB --> PAY : committed
deactivate PDB

... processing ...

PAY --> BR : paymentComplete
deactivate PAY

... waiting for async event ...

BR -> GW : checkStatus()
GW --> BR : status

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 8. SPACERS  |||  and  ||N||
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== Spacers ==

BR -> GW : before spacer
GW --> BR : response

|||

BR -> GW : after single spacer
GW --> BR : response

||50||

BR -> GW : after 50px spacer
GW --> BR : response

||20||

BR -> WA : after 20px spacer
WA --> BR : response

|||

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 9. BOX — all forms
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== Box forms (already declared at top) ==

' Boxes were declared at the top of this diagram.
' Additional interactions to exercise box grouping visibility:

BR -> WA : intra-box (frontend)
WA -> GW : cross-box (FE → BE)
GW -> AU : intra-box (backend)
AU -> OR : intra-box (backend)
OR -> PDB : cross-box (BE → Data)
PDB -> CA : intra-box (data)
CA --> OR : cross-box (Data → BE)
OR --> GW : backend internal
GW --> WA : cross-box
WA --> BR : frontend internal

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 10. REF — reference to external diagram
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== ref (single participant) ==

BR -> GW : triggerRef()

ref over GW : See Authentication\nSubflow Diagram

GW --> BR : triggered

== ref (spanning participants) ==

BR -> OR : complexOperation()

ref over GW, OR
    Order Processing Subflow
    See: order-flow-diagram.puml
    Steps 1-12
end ref

OR --> BR : operation complete

== ref (multi-participant inline) ==

ref over AU, OR, PDB : Data Validation\nRef Diagram

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 11. NEWPAGE
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

newpage

== After newpage (page 2) ==

BR -> GW : first message on page 2
GW --> BR : response on page 2

newpage Titled Second Page

== After newpage with title ==

BR -> AU : auth on titled page 2
AU --> BR : auth response

note over BR, GW
    **Grammar targets:**
    autonumber / autonumber N / autonumber N inc "format"
    autonumber stop / autonumber resume
    dividers, delays, spacing
    box/end box, ref over, newpage
end note

@enduml
